{
  "page": "Stone Mill",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Stone Mill</b>, also called <b>the Stone Mill</b>, is a crossing of the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Fork\" title=\"Red Fork\">Red Fork</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Trident\" title=\"Trident\">Trident</a> in the western <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a>. The location of Stone Mill has not yet been published on maps, although it may be north of <a href=\"/index.php/Pinkmaiden_Castle\" title=\"Pinkmaiden Castle\">Pinkmaiden Castle</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiaf_westeros.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiaf_westeros.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stone_Mill&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stone_Mill&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Stone Mill is the scene of the fiercest fighting during the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Fords\" title=\"Battle of the Fords\">Battle of the Fords</a>. There, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Gregor_Clegane\" title=\"Gregor Clegane\">Gregor Clegane</a> manages to cross the Trident with his best men, but only after heavy losses. He is routed when Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Edmure_Tully\" title=\"Edmure Tully\">Edmure Tully</a> counter-attacks with his reserve.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Leo_Lefford\" title=\"Leo Lefford\">Leo Lefford</a> drowns during the fighting.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stone_Mill&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Harwin\" title=\"Harwin\">Harwin</a> tells <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a> that Gregor reportedly lost half of his men at Stone Mill.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos22.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> \n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/Rymund_the_Rhymer\" title=\"Rymund the Rhymer\">Rymund the Rhymer</a> entertains Edmure, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Marq_Piper\" title=\"Marq Piper\">Marq Piper</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Patrek_Mallister\" title=\"Patrek Mallister\">Patrek Mallister</a> with verses about the battle at the Stone Mill.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos14.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Stone_Mill&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiaf_westeros.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiaf_westeros.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_World_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"A World of Ice and Fire\">George R. R. Martin's A World of Ice and Fire</a></i>,  Westeros.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok45.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_45\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 45\">Chapter 45</a>, Catelyn VI.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasosap